sequenceDiagram
  actor Author
  participant WebApp
  participant AuthService
  participant BlogAPI
  participant PostStore
  participant SearchIndexer

  Author->>WebApp: Publish draft
  WebApp->>AuthService: Validate session
  AuthService-->>WebApp: Session OK
  WebApp->>+BlogAPI: POST /posts/publish
  BlogAPI->>PostStore: Persist published post
  PostStore-->>BlogAPI: Saved
  BlogAPI-)SearchIndexer: Reindex post
  SearchIndexer-->>BlogAPI: Accepted
  BlogAPI-->>-WebApp: 200 Published
  WebApp-->>Author: Post is live
